    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Sam Harris is back this week at @ClubRandom_!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2031044341586854326",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-09T16:28:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Can we all go back and be nicer for a change?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2030136273202286634",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-07T04:19:40+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Trump fired Kristi Noem. He did it by tweet while she was giving a speech. She never saw it coming. Now she knows how her dog felt.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2030133685346054651",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-07T04:09:23+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The music icon @BillyIdol is at @ClubRandom_!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2028867863252185380",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T16:19:27+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Western values are not about oppression.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2027454417805709675",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-27T18:42:56+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": ".@JohnMellencamp this week at @ClubRandom_!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2027454307784933655",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-27T18:42:29+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Democrats don't eat babies.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2026718980027904499",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T18:00:34+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The maturity level of this country is\u2026what\u2019s below one?",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2026494265673789793",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T03:07:38+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Trump just said what I said Friday: the other side never claps for the other team, advertising to the world that the state of our nation is HOPELESSLY DIVIDED.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2026484300120731818",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T02:28:02+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "There\u2019s nothing gay about dressing exactly like him, remember that.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2026479659572219948",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T02:09:35+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Ya see? All this talk about what the president is going to propose to congress? That was my editorial Friday, congress is supposed to propose laws, executive branch is supposed to execute!! Like a Venezuelan drug boat.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2026474980964549082",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T01:51:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
